{"tid":1639100,"cid":38,"subCid":0,"title":"Protestor suffered Intracranial bleeding","createTime":"2019-10-08T13:46:15.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-10T05:37:44.000Z","uid":48083,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"7a9cbd2bfd809ff18ece41d5802d4135903b17dc","tid":1639100,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T13:46:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Nyy3kat.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FNyy3kat.jpg&h=a09303b7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nThis is reported by the doctor. <br />\nThis is Caused by police brutality <br />\nMedical treatment is delayed by 6 hrs<br />\nFurther delay could be fatal<br />\n(Source: Anti-extradition law Telegram )<br />\n<br />\n有醫生聯絡本頻道，披露警方濫暴情況。他透露，有一位青年示威者遭警方以警棍毆打頭部，導致顱內出血，血塊佔腦部相當大面積，需要立即進行手術取出血塊。該醫生指出，警察拖延傷者送院，由被打至送院足足延遲逾6小時，若再耽誤傷者恐變成植物人，甚至可能死亡。傷者現時於屯門醫院深切治療部留醫，仍未完全清醒。 <br />\n<br />\n該醫生進一步表示，即使是殺人犯，面對的處罰亦只是收監，「究竟呢個青年做咗啲乜要受咁嘅對待？當社會大眾譴責示威者破壞港鐵措施，又有幾多人會譴責警方使用嘅過分武力？講緊係蓄意令人受傷甚至死亡嘅武力。」 他呼籲警方不要再對任何人的頭部使用警棍及其他武力。<br />\n<br />\n圖為該醫生參照傷者傷勢製作的X光片示意圖，紅圈為血塊。<br />\n<br />\n（轉載請註明出處：反送中已核實資訊頻道@<a href=\"https://t.me/antiextraditionverifiednews）\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fantiextraditionverifiednews%EF%BC%89&d=cH2nQL%2B7gNVGRZzFZPB6VhnxOJLX742lx1SCoot1iYY%3D&h=93c36c45\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/antiextraditionverifiednews）</a>"},{"pid":"e2c399a6387e33fcf3a1d18dea1d81121eeb00b5","tid":1639100,"uid":53666,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T15:59:43.000Z","msg":"Brutal police is now under no control<br />\n<br />\nthey are like hyena looking for prays on the street everyday.<br />\nWith now the anti-mask law passed, they can arrest any one wearing a mask.<br />\n<br />\nIf you don't believe, look at this:<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">Random arrest of mask-wearing student and a passer-by,</span><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/gro